## Scope
- In scope: src/pages/Inventory/**, shared components used by Inventory.
- Out of scope: packages/server/ unless explicitly asked.

## Current APIs
- GET /api/products, GET /api/products/:id, PUT /api/products/:id
- GET /api/products/:id/transactions, POST /api/products/:id/transactions
- GET /api/vat/calculate, POST /api/invoices

## Jarvis behaviours
- Filter by lowStock query param when linked from Dashboard
- Pre-fill sell price suggestion from comps when editing
- Empty state: "Add from Evaluator or create a product manually"
